		title,

	),

	joinType:'left',
	matchType:'exact',
	ignoreSpaces: false,
	broadcast: 'auto')~> Join1

		{_id},
		cohortid,
		{states.id},
		{state.status},
		{state.type},
		value,
		Custom,
		completionTime),
	count = count('1')) ~> aggregate1

		{_id},
		journeyname,
		cohortid,
		{states.id},
		{state.status},
		{state.type},
		value,
		Custom,
		completionTime
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> select1

Constantvalue window(asc(Constant_value, true),
	RowNumber = rowNumber()) ~> AddRownumber
AddRownumber filter(RowNumber<500) ~> TempFilterTest
TempFilterTest sink(allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true,
	mapColumn(
		{_id} = RowNumber,
		journeyname,
		cohortid,
		id = {states.id},
		status = {state.status},
		type = {state.type},
		value,
		completionTime
	)) ~> sink1

source(output(
		title as string,
		journey as (key as string, value as string)[]
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: false,
	validateSchema: true,
	ignoreNoFilesFound: false,
	documentForm: 'documentPerLine') ~> journeystructure
source(output(
		{_id} as ({$oid} as string),
		journeys as (journeyName as string, cohortId as string, revisions as ({1} as (states as (id as string, state as string, type as string, completionTime as string)[])))[],
		email as string
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: false,
	validateSchema: true,
	ignoreNoFilesFound: false,
	documentForm: 'documentPerLine') ~> mondelezmongodbusers
journeystructure foldDown(unroll(journey, journey),
	mapColumn(
		title,
		key = journey.key,
		value = journey.value
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: false,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: false) ~> Flatten1
mondelezmongodbusers foldDown(unroll(journeys, journeys),
	mapColumn(
		{_id},
		journeyname = journeys.journeyName,
		email,
		cohortid = journeys.cohortId,
		states = journeys.revisions.{1}.states,
		revisions = journeys.revisions
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: false,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: false) ~> Flatten2
Filter3 foldDown(unroll(states, states),
	mapColumn(
		{_id},
		journeyname,
		email,
		cohortid,
		{states.id} = states.id,
		{state.status} = states.state,
		{state.type} = states.type
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: false,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: false) ~> Flatten3
Flatten3, Filter1 join({states.id} == Custom,
	joinType:'left',
	matchType:'exact',
	ignoreSpaces: false,
	broadcast: 'auto')~> Join1
Flatten1 derive(Custom = regexReplace(key, '[^0-9]','')) ~> DerivedColumn1
DerivedColumn1 filter(Custom != "") ~> Filter1
Join1 filter(value!="" && length(value) <50) ~> Filter2
Filter2 alterRow(upsertIf(true())) ~> AlterRow1
Flatten2 filter(email == "gunjan.dadhich@bts.com") ~> Filter3
AlterRow1 sink(allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	deletable:true,
	insertable:true,
	updateable:true,
	upsertable:true,
	rowRelativeUrl: 'journeyname',
	insertHttpMethod: 'POST',
	deleteHttpMethod: 'DELETE',
	upsertHttpMethod: 'PUT',
	updateHttpMethod: 'PATCH',
	timeout: 30,
	requestInterval: 0,
	requestFormat: ['type' -> 'json', 'outputDateFormat' -> 'MM/dd/yyyy', 'outputTimestampFormat' -> 'MM/dd/yyyy HH:mm:ss'],
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true,
	mapColumn(
		{_id},
		journeyname,
		email,
		cohortid,
		id = {states.id},
		status = {state.status},
		type = {state.type},
		title,
		key,
		value,
		Custom
	)) ~> sink2
